---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Molten" description="Molten's privacy policy - your data stays private and secure">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="gradient-orange text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-6">ðŸ”’</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90">
        Last updated: October 23, 2025
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Commitment to Your Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          At Molten, we believe your creative work and inventory data should remain completely private.
          We've designed the app from the ground up with privacy as a core principle, not an afterthought.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          <strong>Simple summary:</strong> Your data stays on your devices. We don't collect it, we don't sell it,
          we don't even see it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- What We Don't Collect -->
      <div class="mb-12 bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">What We DON'T Collect</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600">âœ—</span>
            <span>We don't collect your inventory data</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600">âœ—</span>
            <span>We don't track your usage patterns</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600">âœ—</span>
            <span>We don't use analytics or tracking services</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600">âœ—</span>
            <span>We don't sell your data to third parties</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600">âœ—</span>
            <span>We don't use advertising networks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600">âœ—</span>
            <span>We don't require account creation or login</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Data Storage -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Where Your Data Lives</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Local Storage</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
              All your inventory data, photos, notes, and records are stored locally on your device using
              Apple's Core Data framework. This data never leaves your device unless you explicitly choose to sync it.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">iCloud Sync (Optional)</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-3">
              If you enable iCloud sync, your data is synchronized between your devices using Apple's CloudKit
              framework. This means:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg text-gray-700 ml-4">
              <li>Your data syncs directly between your devices via your personal iCloud account</li>
              <li>We never have access to your iCloud data</li>
              <li>Apple encrypts your data in transit and at rest</li>
              <li>Only you can access this data through your Apple ID</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Photos</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
              Custom photos you upload for glass items or projects are stored in your device's local storage
              and backed up to iCloud (if you have iCloud backup enabled for the app). These photos are never
              sent to our servers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What We Do Collect (Minimal) -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Information We May Receive</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">App Store Information</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
              When you download Molten from the App Store, Apple may share basic analytics with us such as
              number of downloads and crash reports. This data is anonymized and cannot be linked to individual users.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Support Communications</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
              If you contact us via email for support, we retain your email and the content of your message
              to help resolve your issue. We never share this information with third parties.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Your Rights -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Since your data is stored locally on your device and in your personal iCloud account:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-orange-500">âœ“</span>
            <span>You have complete control over your data</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-orange-500">âœ“</span>
            <span>You can delete the app and all its data at any time</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-orange-500">âœ“</span>
            <span>You can disable iCloud sync in your device settings</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-orange-500">âœ“</span>
            <span>You own all your inventory data, photos, and notes</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Third-Party Services -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Molten does not integrate with any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.
          The only third-party service we use is Apple's infrastructure:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg text-gray-700 ml-4">
          <li>CloudKit for optional iCloud sync</li>
          <li>App Store for distribution</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-4">
          These services are governed by Apple's privacy policy, which you can review at
          <a href="https://www.apple.com/privacy/" class="text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-600 underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            apple.com/privacy
          </a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Children's Privacy -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Molten is not directed at children under 13. Since we don't collect personal information from anyone,
          we don't knowingly collect information from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected
          information from a child, please contact us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Changes to Privacy Policy -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg text-gray-700 ml-4">
          <li>Posting the new policy on this page</li>
          <li>Updating the "Last Updated" date at the top</li>
          <li>Notifying you via the app if the changes are significant</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-4">
          We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any changes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          If you have questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your data, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          <a href="mailto:info@moltenglass.app" class="text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-600 font-bold">
            info@moltenglass.app
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 gradient-orange text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Your Privacy Matters</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-white/90">
        Download Molten and experience truly private inventory management.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/molten"
           class="bg-white text-orange-500 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
          Download on App Store
        </a>
        <a href="/features"
           class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition border-2 border-white/30">
          Explore Features
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
